    npx:hasSignature "HAHZJMns8TmElABDJXLlEl7YyI7nUpR5PFtSTvt6+rRFRXqP8pA9VjaXZ4qUmHUmcSYGsDxKjSXoZVsdNFDxF+lWmC+ZflFufg6KdlCdyyNZyYFsM8fSpPIt6ErftBoGqGx/XJWwvcbN3QXhO1uUKbUS2MGr5X/9ObeZxY5Za8k=";
